  "response_text": "A red theater curtain fills the screen with the yellow “Danimals” logo centered above the words “PRESENTS:” in white. The curtains part to reveal a sunny backyard behind them. A young boy stands on a low stone retaining wall beside stone steps, wearing oversized turquoise swim goggles, a red-and-yellow striped T-shirt, teal shorts, and sneakers. Over the backyard image, the “Danimals Presents” text remains briefly, and an animated cartoon monkey appears at the right, grinning and tumbling in with a small basket of red fruit.\n\nThe boy is now fully visible in the yard, standing upright on the stone wall with bright green grass and a wooden fence behind him. He holds a small Danimals-style drink bottle to his mouth and drinks while wearing the swim goggles. The patio below him is wet, with a large muddy puddle spread across the concrete near a black garden hose and a round drain grate. He continues drinking for several moments, facing forward, relaxed and steady on the wall.\n\nA large snorkel tube appears attached to his goggles, curving down in front of his chest with a blue mouthpiece area and a yellow tube. He lifts it upright, then shifts his weight and looks down toward the wet patio below. He bends his knees, raises one arm with the snorkel, and prepares to jump from the stone wall. He steps off into the puddle, landing feet-first and then dropping out of view in a big splash of muddy water. Water sprays upward and outward across the concrete.\n\nAfter the splash, the boy is no longer visible. The camera remains on the empty wet patio as ripples spread through the muddy puddle. The stone wall, steps, black hose, and drain remain in place while the water settles.\n\nThe commercial ends on a bright illustrated product display. On green grass under a blue sky, several Danimals products are arranged in front of a whimsical treehouse built into a large tree. The packaging includes a red multi-pack labeled “Danimals Smoothie” with “Bananaberry” visible, a smiling single bottle with a cartoon face and soccer ball, and a white-and-red package labeled “Super Danimals.” Small fine print runs along the bottom, while a soft yellow “Danimals” mark floats in the sky-like background.",
